okay um it’s the coyote and roadrunner story ?
and it starts off with a desert scene
and the coyote is chasing the roadrunner
with a fork and a knife
’cause he wants to eat him
and then he can’t catch the roadrunner
so he tries to come up with a plan ?
aand his first plan is
to attach a boxing glove to a spring
and then when the roadrunner passes by
he’s gonna let go of the spring
and the boxing glove is gonna knock the roadrunner out
and the roadrunner comes by
and he lets go of the spring
but it the thing it eventually backfires on him
and he actually like gets thrown into the cliff backwards ?
and the boxing glove punches him
and the second plan is
to suspend a tightrope
and like hang an anvil from it ?
so that when the roadrunner comes by he’s gonna hit into it
so he walks across the tightrope with the anvil
but then the rope is weighted down by the anvil
so he he falls down
and the roadrunner comes by and taunts him
and goes away
and and uh thee coyote becomes frustrated
he lets go of the anvil
and he gets like thrown into the air ?
and then he comes back down and hits the ground
and then the third plan is
to uh go into the mines and catch him there
’cause it’s really dark
soo they both go into the mines
and they’re both chasing around each other in circles
and and the roadrunner I mean
the coyote can’t catch up with the roadrunner
and then uh basically they chase each other around
and the roadrunner keeps taunting him
the roadrunner goes away
